OL,5, Amazon is facing an investigation by   
OL,6, the US Congress over its warehouse     
OL,7, safety practices, adding to pressure it
OL,8, faces over its treatment of workers.   
OL,10,FSenator Bernie Sanders announced the   
OL,11,Fprobe, calling the company one of      
OL,12,FAmerica's "most dangerous" employers.  
OL,14,FHe pointed to a recent report which    
OL,15,Ffound that injury rates at Amazon      
OL,16,Fwarehouses in the US are higher than at
OL,17,Fsimilar facilities.                    
OL,19,FAmazon said it disagreed with the      
OL,20,Fclaims.                                
